  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bbe\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Change is necessary in the healthcare sector",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe has announced that an immediate policy change is necessary in the health sector during a discussion with the Government Medical Officers Association.",
        "The report of the three-member committee appointed by the association to investigate the shortage of drugs in the country was handed over to President Ranil Wickremesinghe at the Presidential Secretariat on Saturday (03).",
        "The President emphasized the need for an immediate mechanism to alleviate the hardships faced by the people due to shortage of medicines and increase in prices of medicines.",
        "He also mentioned that he is going to discuss with the World Bank and the International Monetary Fund regarding other needs of the health sector including medicines.",
        "The President also said that it is necessary to develop additional facilities at Colombo National Hospital, Kalupovila Teaching Hospital and Jayawardenapura Hospital.",
        "President Ranil Wickremesinghe pointed out that policy change is necessary for the entire health sector.",
        "The representatives of the association requested the President that there is a shortage of drugs and insulin for cancer patients and to take immediate steps to solve this problem."
      ],
